title: Photos: Surprise, surprise: Antoine Roussel gets into a scrap; Stars top Flyers 2-1
text: Oct 20, 2015; Philadelphia, PA, USA; NHL linesman Jay Sharrers (57) separates Dallas Stars left wing Antoine Roussel (21) and Philadelphia Flyers center Sean Couturier (14) during the third period at Wells Fargo Center.
